  "root_text": {
    "an7.31:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7.31 ",
    "an7.31:0.2": "3. Vajjisattakavagga ",
    "an7.31:0.3": "Parābhavasutta ",
    "an7.31:1.1": "“Sattime, bhikkhave, upāsakassa parābhavā …pe… ",
    "an7.31:1.2": "sattime, bhikkhave, upāsakassa sambhavā. ",
    "an7.31:1.3": "Katame satta? ",
    "an7.31:1.4": "Bhikkhudassanaṁ na hāpeti, ",
    "an7.31:1.5": "saddhammassavanaṁ nappamajjati, ",
    "an7.31:1.6": "adhisīle sikkhati, ",
    "an7.31:1.7": "pasādabahulo hoti, ",
    "an7.31:1.8": "bhikkhūsu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca anupārambhacitto dhammaṁ suṇāti na randhagavesī, ",
    "an7.31:1.9": "na ito bahiddhā dakkhiṇeyyaṁ gavesati, ",
    "an7.31:1.10": "idha ca pubbakāraṁ karoti. ",
    "an7.31:1.11": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta upāsakassa sambhavāti. ",
    "an7.31:2.1": "Dassanaṁ bhāvitattānaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:2.2": "Yo hāpeti upāsako; ",
    "an7.31:2.3": "Savanañca ariyadhammānaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:2.4": "Adhisīle na sikkhati. ",
    "an7.31:3.1": "Appasādo ca bhikkhūsu, ",
    "an7.31:3.2": "bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaḍḍhati; ",
    "an7.31:3.3": "Upārambhakacitto ca, ",
    "an7.31:3.4": "saddhammaṁ sotumicchati. ",
    "an7.31:4.1": "Ito ca bahiddhā aññaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:4.2": "dakkhiṇeyyaṁ gavesati; ",
    "an7.31:4.3": "Tattheva ca pubbakāraṁ, ",
    "an7.31:4.4": "yo karoti upāsako. ",
    "an7.31:5.1": "Ete kho parihāniye, ",
    "an7.31:5.2": "satta dhamme sudesite; ",
    "an7.31:5.3": "Upāsako sevamāno, ",
    "an7.31:5.4": "saddhammā parihāyati. ",
    "an7.31:6.1": "Dassanaṁ bhāvitattānaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:6.2": "Yo na hāpeti upāsako; ",
    "an7.31:6.3": "Savanañca ariyadhammānaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:6.4": "Adhisīle ca sikkhati. ",
    "an7.31:7.1": "Pasādo cassa bhikkhūsu, ",
    "an7.31:7.2": "bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaḍḍhati; ",
    "an7.31:7.3": "Anupārambhacitto ca, ",
    "an7.31:7.4": "saddhammaṁ sotumicchati. ",
    "an7.31:8.1": "Na ito bahiddhā aññaṁ, ",
    "an7.31:8.2": "dakkhiṇeyyaṁ gavesati; ",
    "an7.31:8.3": "Idheva ca pubbakāraṁ, ",
    "an7.31:8.4": "yo karoti upāsako. ",
    "an7.31:9.1": "Ete kho aparihāniye, ",
    "an7.31:9.2": "Satta dhamme sudesite; ",
    "an7.31:9.3": "Upāsako sevamāno, ",
    "an7.31:9.4": "Saddhammā na parihāyatī”ti. ",
    "an7.31:9.5": "Ekādasamaṁ. ",
    "an7.31:9.6": "Vajjisattakavaggo tatiyo. ",
    "an7.31:10.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "an7.31:10.1": "Sāranda vassakāro ca, ",
    "an7.31:10.2": "tisattakāni bhikkhukā; ",
    "an7.31:10.3": "Bodhisaññā dve ca hāni, ",
    "an7.31:10.4": "vipatti ca parābhavoti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an7.31:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 7.31 ",
    "an7.31:0.2": "3. The Vajji Seven ",
    "an7.31:0.3": "Downfalls for a Lay Follower ",
    "an7.31:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these seven downfalls for a lay follower … ",
    "an7.31:1.2": "There are these seven successes for a lay follower. ",
    "an7.31:1.3": "What seven? ",
    "an7.31:1.4": "They don’t miss out on seeing the mendicants. ",
    "an7.31:1.5": "They don’t neglect listening to the true teaching. ",
    "an7.31:1.6": "They train in higher ethical conduct. ",
    "an7.31:1.7": "They’re very confident about mendicants, whether senior, junior, or middle. ",
    "an7.31:1.8": "They don’t listen to the teaching with a hostile, fault-finding mind. ",
    "an7.31:1.9": "They don’t seek outside of the Buddhist community for those worthy of religious donations. ",
    "an7.31:1.10": "And they serve the Buddhist community first. ",
    "an7.31:1.11": "These are the seven successes for a lay follower. ",
    "an7.31:2.1": "A lay follower misses out on seeing ",
    "an7.31:2.2": "those who are evolved ",
    "an7.31:2.3": "and listening to the teachings of the Noble One. ",
    "an7.31:2.4": "They don’t train in higher ethical conduct, ",
    "an7.31:3.1": "and their suspicion about mendicants ",
    "an7.31:3.2": "just grows and grows. ",
    "an7.31:3.3": "They want to listen to the true teaching ",
    "an7.31:3.4": "with a fault-finding mind. ",
    "an7.31:4.1": "They seek outside the Buddhist community ",
    "an7.31:4.2": "for someone else worthy of religious donations, ",
    "an7.31:4.3": "and that lay follower ",
    "an7.31:4.4": "serves them first. ",
    "an7.31:5.1": "These seven principles leading to decline ",
    "an7.31:5.2": "have been well taught. ",
    "an7.31:5.3": "A lay follower who practices these ",
    "an7.31:5.4": "falls away from the true teaching. ",
    "an7.31:6.1": "A lay follower doesn’t miss out on seeing ",
    "an7.31:6.2": "those who are evolved ",
    "an7.31:6.3": "and listening to the teachings of the Noble One. ",
    "an7.31:6.4": "They train in higher ethical conduct, ",
    "an7.31:7.1": "and their confidence in mendicants ",
    "an7.31:7.2": "just grows and grows. ",
    "an7.31:7.3": "They want to listen to the true teaching ",
    "an7.31:7.4": "without a fault-finding mind. ",
    "an7.31:8.1": "They don’t seek outside the Buddhist community ",
    "an7.31:8.2": "for someone else worthy of religious donations, ",
    "an7.31:8.3": "and that lay follower ",
    "an7.31:8.4": "serves the Buddhist community first. ",
    "an7.31:9.1": "These seven principles that prevent decline ",
    "an7.31:9.2": "have been well taught. ",
    "an7.31:9.3": "A lay follower who practices them ",
    "an7.31:9.4": "doesn’t fall away from the true teaching.” ",
